Description: Tool for import and process data from Brazilian COVID-19 Portal (<https://covid.saude.gov.br>). The Brazilian government keeps an extensive database for sharing information on the COVID-19 epidemiological condition. Daily, the Ministry of Health (Ministerio da Saude) updates and publicly disseminates these data. Some information that can be obtained: cases, deaths, and recoveries for each Brazilian region, municipality and state.
